        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1433763806" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10635774335785688121">I marked it 5 because reading this book was an excellent journey towards the children&apos;s world! I learned a lot about the children&apos;s psychological needs and about their world. I was really astonished that this book was written more than 100 years ago because unfortunately Maria Montessori deliberately and accurately addressed problems our schools still suffer from. The Montessori method gives a lot of solutions for the problems in our schools. I truly wish that this method will be more adopted by</span>
  <span id="freeText10635774335785688121" style="display:none">I marked it 5 because reading this book was an excellent journey towards the children's world! I learned a lot about the children's psychological needs and about their world. I was really astonished that this book was written more than 100 years ago because unfortunately Maria Montessori deliberately and accurately addressed problems our schools still suffer from. The Montessori method gives a lot of solutions for the problems in our schools. I truly wish that this method will be more adopted by schools in the Arab world because education should be way more than giving students knowledge and sending them home!!! </span>
