<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer11074095953828168803">Maria Montessori was an Italian physician, educator, philosopher, humanitarian and devout Catholic; she is best known for her philosophy and the Montessori method of education of children from birth to adolescence. Her educational method is in use today in a number of public as well as private schools throughout the world.</span>

</div>
